Reasoning: The paper deals with regression using machine learning techniques, specifically Conditional GAN and optimal transport cost minimization. This falls under the broad category of machine learning and can be classified under several sub-categories. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category as it deals with the core concepts of machine learning. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as it deals with the application of machine learning in creating intelligent systems. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is another likely sub-category as it deals with the application of machine learning in image and video analysis, which is a common use case for regression. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SY (Systems and Control) are also possible sub-categories as they deal with the optimization and control aspects of machine learning models.
